<br>
Of course, the warrior was very well-geared with a lot of AA (high AC, defensive skills, he's a real stickler on tweaking his DPS and stats) and everyone else was pretty well stacked in the gear department, so this setup might not be best for pickup groups of people with velious armor and holes filled in by bazaar items. <p><a href="http://home.elp.rr.com/scythek/everquest/">Tuis Kagato</a> - Arch Convoker of Karana (<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=175764">Profile</a>) - <a href="http://www.pandemonium.cc/">Deloth's Dudes</a><br>
